   Eastern Airlines and Continental Airlines have
announced new cut-rate fares for children and senior citizens for
the summer, and at least one other major airline quickly followed
suit.
   The two airlines also said Monday they were easing some
restrictions now attached to regular ``MaxSaver'' deep-discount
